premise_source_doc_sentence: A nut roast or roasted nut loaf is a rich and savoury vegetarian dish consisting of nuts , grains , vegetable oils , broth or butter , and seasonings formed into a firm loaf shape or long casserole dish before roasting and often eaten as an alternative to a traditional British style roast dinner .
It is also broadly consumed during fasting days as it is a strict vegetarian dish .
Buddha 's delight , often transliterated as Luóhàn zhāi , lo han jai , or lo hon jai , is a vegetarian dish well known in Chinese and Buddhist cuisine .
The vegetarian dish Rajma chawal is very similar  (  which translates literally to red beans and rice  )  , popular in North India .
Rājmā or Rāzmā is a popular South Asian vegetarian dish consisting of red kidney beans in a thick gravy with many Indian whole spices and usually served with rice and food .
